pma:database.name: seven
pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `day` ( `store_id` int(20) NOT NULL, `store_latitude` double NOT NULL, `store_longitude` double NOT NULL, `date` date NOT NULL, `tempC` int(20) NOT NULL, `tempF` int(20) NOT NULL, `windspeedMiles` int(20) NOT NULL, `windspeedKmph` int(20) NOT NULL, `winddirDegree` int(20) NOT NULL, `winddir16Point` varchar(999) NOT NULL, `weatherCode` int(20) NOT NULL, `weatherIconUrl` varchar(999) NOT NULL, `weatherDesc` varchar(999) NOT NULL, `precipMM` double NOT NULL, `humidity` int(20) NOT NULL, `visibility` int(20) NOT NULL, `pressure` int(20) NOT NULL, `cloudcover` int(20) NOT NULL ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `night` ( `store_id` int(20) NOT NULL, `store_latitude` double NOT NULL, `store_longitude` double NOT NULL, `date` date NOT NULL, `tempC` int(20) NOT NULL, `tempF` int(20) NOT NULL, `windspeedMiles` int(20) NOT NULL, `windspeedKmph` int(20) NOT NULL, `winddirDegree` int(20) NOT NULL, `winddir16Point` varchar(999) NOT NULL, `weatherCode` int(20) NOT NULL, `weatherIconUrl` varchar(999) NOT NULL, `weatherDesc` varchar(999) NOT NULL, `precipMM` double NOT NULL, `humidity` int(20) NOT NULL, `visibility` int(20) NOT NULL, `pressure` int(20) NOT NULL, `cloudcover` int(20) NOT NULL ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `store` ( `store_id` int(20) NOT NULL, `store_name` varchar(999) NOT NULL, `store_latitude` double NOT NULL, `store_longitude` double NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`store_id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;
